Mathematics, Statistics, and Computer Science






Mathematics, Statistics, and Computer Science
Thank you for your interest in giving to UIC’s Department of Mathematics, Statistics, and Computer Science (MSCS). Your gift may be designated to any of the MSCS or College of Liberal Arts and Sciences (LAS) funds below. To provide general support to MSCS and its students, please direct your gift to the Mathematics, Statistics and Computer Science Fund. Detailed descriptions of each MSCS fund.






